<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{service.title}} - Unterlagenliste</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .generated-info {
            background: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
        }
        
        .generated-info span {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .section h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .section h2::before {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .contact h2::before { content: "📞"; }
        .documents h2::before { content: "📋"; }
        .cost h2::before { content: "💰"; }
        .privacy h2::before { content: "🔒"; }
        
        .office-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        
        .office-details h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .detail-row strong {
            min-width: 80px;
            color: #34495e;
        }
        
        .hours-table {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .hours-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        .hours-row:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .hours-row strong {
            min-width: 60px;
        }
        
        .document-list {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .document-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .checkbox {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #27ae60;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            margin-top: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .cost-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        }
        
        .privacy-notice {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .qr-placeholder {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: #ecf0f1;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px auto;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .qr-placeholder::before {
            content: "QR";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        /* Print styles */
        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .container {
                box-shadow: none;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header {
                background: #2c3e50 !important;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            }
            
            .section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
        
        /* Mobile responsive */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .detail-row strong {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{{service.title}}</h1>
            <p>{{service.description}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Generated Info -->
        <div class="generated-info">
            <span>📅 Erstellt: {{createdAt}} | Gültig bis: {{expiresAt}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Contact Information -->
            <div class="section contact">
                <h2>Kontaktinformationen</h2>
                <div class="office-details">
                    <h3>{{office.name}}</h3>
                    
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>📍 Adresse:</strong>
                        <span>{{office.address}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>📞 Telefon:</strong>
                        <span>{{office.phone}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>🌐 Website:</strong>
                        <span>{{office.website}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>🕒 Öffnungszeiten:</strong>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="hours-table">
                        {{#each office.hours}}
                        <div class="hours-row">
                            <strong>{{@key}}:</strong>
                            <span>{{this}}</span>
                        </div>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Required Documents -->
            <div class="section documents">
                <h2>Benötigte Unterlagen</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #7f8c8d;">
                    Bitte bringen Sie alle folgenden Dokumente mit:
                </p>
                
                <ul class="document-list">
                    {{#each service.documents}}
                    <li class="document-item">
                        <div class="checkbox"></div>
                        <span>{{this}}</span>
                    </li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Cost Information -->
            <div class="section cost">
                <h2>Kosten & Zahlung</h2>
                <div class="cost-info">
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>💰 Gebühr:</strong>
                        <span>{{service.cost}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <strong>💳 Zahlung:</strong>
                        <span>{{service.paymentMethods}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Privacy Notice -->
            <div class="section privacy">
                <h2>Datenschutzhinweis (DSGVO)</h2>
                <div class="privacy-notice">
                    <p>
                        <strong>Datenverarbeitung:</strong> Ihre Telefonnummer wurde temporär gespeichert, 
                        um Ihnen diesen Link zu senden, und wird innerhalb von 48 Stunden automatisch gelöscht.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <strong>Gültigkeit:</strong> Diese Seite läuft am {{expiresAt}} ab und wird automatisch entfernt.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                        <strong>Ihre Rechte:</strong> Sie haben das Recht auf Auskunft, Berichtigung und Löschung 
                        Ihrer Daten. Bei Fragen wenden Sie sich an die jeweilige Zulassungsstelle.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="qr-placeholder"></div>
            <p>Digitaler Assistent der KFZ-Zulassungsstelle</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7; margin-top: 5px;">
                Session: {{sessionId}} | Generiert: {{createdAt}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>